| ID | Component Name        | Description/Purpose                                 | Qty | Unit Cost ($) | Total Cost ($) | Vendor    | Product Link                                  | Status     |
|----|------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|-----|----------------|-----------------|-----------|------------------------------------------------|------------|
