| 2  | Soil Moisture Sensor   | Capacitive soil sensor (from 2-pack)                | 1   | $4.49         | $4.49           | Amazon    | https://tinyurl.com/3598na4e                  | Purchased  |
| 3  | DHT22 Sensor           | Temperature & humidity monitoring (from 3-pack)     | 1   | $2.33         | $2.33           | Amazon    | https://tinyurl.com/5899c3ms                  | Purchased  |
| 4  | LDR + 10k Resistor     | Light dependent resistor (from 10-pack)             | 1   | $0.50         | $0.50           | Amazon    | https://tinyurl.com/mwpdzevu                  | Purchased  |
